      "specialNote": "Stores HTML-formatted text. Default allowedFormats: BOLD, ITALIC, UNDERLINE, STRIKETHROUGH, LINK, NUMBERED_LIST, BULLETED_LIST (excludes SUBSCRIPT, SUPERSCRIPT, TEXT_ALIGNMENT, TABLE). To display styled text editor values in read-only mode, use a!styledTextEditorField with readOnly: true (NOT richTextDisplayField). For grid display, use stripHtml() on a separate database field."
